`, `analyzerAgent`, `preparerAgent`, `analyzerPreparerAgent`, `hooksPreparerAgent`, `hooksAnalyzerPreparerAgent`, `hooksAnalyzerAgent`, `fullAgent`) with a single `wrappedAgent` that:\\n- Forwards all `agent.Agent` methods to `ea`\\n- Implements ALL optional interface methods (forwarding to `ea`)\\n- Implements `CapabilityDeclarer`, returning caps converted from `ea.info.Capabilities`\\n\\n`Wrap()` becomes:\\n```go\\nfunc Wrap(ea *Agent) agent.Agent {\\n    caps := ea.info.Capabilities\\n    return &wrappedAgent{\\n        ea: ea,\\n        caps: agent.DeclaredCaps{\\n            Hooks:                  caps.Hooks,\\n            TranscriptAnalyzer:     caps.TranscriptAnalyzer,\\n            TranscriptPreparer:     caps.TranscriptPreparer,\\n            TokenCalculator:        caps.TokenCalculator,\\n            TextGenerator:          caps.TextGenerator,\\n            HookResponseWriter:     caps.HookResponseWriter,\\n            SubagentAwareExtractor: caps.SubagentAwareExtractor,\\n        },\\n    }\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### 4. Update call sites (mechanical — 22 production sites)\\n\\nReplace `ag.(agent.X)` with `agent.AsX(ag)`:\\n\\n| File | Sites | Interfaces |\\n|------|-------|-----------|\\n| `setup.go` | 5 | HookSupport |\\n| `lifecycle.go` | 5 | HookResponseWriter, TranscriptPreparer, TranscriptAnalyzer, SubagentAwareExtractor |\\n| `strategy/manual_commit_hooks.go` | 4 | TranscriptPreparer, TranscriptAnalyzer |\\n| `agent/token_usage.go` | 2 | SubagentAwareExtractor, TokenCalculator (no `agent.` prefix — same package) |\\n| `config.go` | 1 | HookSupport |\\n| `hook_registry.go` | 1 | HookSupport |\\n| `hooks_cmd.go` | 1 | HookSupport |\\n| `state.go` | 1 | TranscriptAnalyzer |\\n| `strategy/common.go` | 1 | TranscriptPreparer |\\n| `setup_test.go` | 2 | HookSupport |\\n\\n### 5. Update `cmd/entire/cli/agent/external/external_test.go`\\n\\nChange all direct type assertions (`wrapped.(agent.HookSupport)`) to use `agent.AsHookSupport(wrapped)` etc. The wrapped agen